							is thoroughly cleaned and tested for moisture content.
						</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Mechanical surface profiling (not just acid etching)</li>
							<li>Oil and contaminant removal</li>
							<li>Crack repair and patching</li>
							<li>Moisture testing and mitigation</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

