						<h3>Decorative Elements</h3>
						<p>
							<strong>Aesthetic Enhancement:</strong> If selected, decorative flakes, metallic effects, or custom patterns are applied 
							while the base coat is still wet for optimal integration and adhesion.
						</p>
						<ul>
							<li>Decorative flake broadcast (if selected)</li>
							<li>Metallic pigment application</li>
							<li>Custom pattern creation</li>
							<li>Excess material removal</li>
						</ul>
					</div>
				</div>

				<div class="process-step">
					<div class="step-number">5</div>
					<div class="step-content">
						<h3>Top Coat Sealing</h3>
						<p>
							<strong>Protection Layer:</strong> A clear, high-performance topcoat provides chemical resistance, UV protection, 
